  "body": "#### System information\n\nGeth version: `1.4.3`\nOS & Version: OSX\n#### Expected behaviour\n\n{\n  \"id\":1,\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"result\": \"0x2ac19db245478a06032e69cdbd2b54e648b78431d0a47bd1fbab18f79f820ba407466e37adbe9e84541cab97ab7d290f4a64a5825c876d22109f3bf813254e8601\"\n}\n\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/wiki/wiki/JSON-RPC#eth_sign\n#### Actual behaviour\n\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"error\":{\"code\":-32602,\"message\":\"common: unmarshalJSON failed: hash must be exactly 32 bytes\"}}\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\n\nUpgraded to 1.4.3 from 1.3.6 curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8545 -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_sign\",\"params\":[\"0xd1ade25ccd3d550a7eb532ac759cac7be09c2719\", \"Schoolbus\"],\"id\":1}'\n",
